    <description>
        <p>
            Listen 1 can search and play songs from many major music sites, making your music
            library more comprehensive. And supports the collection function, conveniently create
            your own song list.
        </p>
	<p>Supported music platforms:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>NetEase Cloud Music</li>
            <li>QQ Music</li>
            <li>Kugou Music</li>
            <li>Kuwo Music</li>
            <li>bilibili</li>
            <li>Migu Music</li>
            <li>Qian Qian Music</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
